<br>
My goal would be to get all the mages who are missing only a few pieces together and get all of them the staff. Also all must go till all have the staff is what I would hope for, but even on CT there were problems. Fortunatly though magi is preaty easy, and even a solid group can do him in if we have a good puller. <br>
<br>
This week I am workign alot, and probably next week to but I will look to organize this as best as possible so that in 2 weeks or if we are lucky less we can take over hate, and get every mage on the server a hate staff =) <br>
<br>
Also we would go whenever possible, as often as we think magi is up, however we will not step on teh toes of raiding guilds. If a guild has a day reserved we will check with them first, but I am hoping we can get all mages to have a fair chance at the staff without having to bug there guild into constant trips. <br>
<br>
